import Header from '../components/Header'
import '../index.css'

function Home() {
    return (
        <>
            <Header />
            <main className="h-screen flex justify-center p-56">
                <form className="bg-black p-10 flex flex-col items-center rounded-lg text-white">
                    <label>Nom d'utilisateur :</label>
                    <input type="text" name="userId" />
                    <input type="submit" value="Envoyer" />
                </form>
            </main>
        </>
    )
}

export default Home
